data.description:
House is an excellent condition! Appliances included (GE Cafe refrigerator, Microwave, Oven, Dishwasher, LG washer and dryer) A jetted tub in master bathroom.
3 car garages! Require minimum of 1 year contact. Utilities paid by tenants Tenants will be responsible for landscaping and other maintenances No pets allowed. **This property is currently occupied, Please do NOT disturb current tenants**
Showing will be available after July 3rd to protect my current tenants. Sorry for the inconveniences ** Showing schedules ** July 3rd, July 4th and every Wednesday and Sundays after that.

1 year minimum.
